snippet.title: Nubs! - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Here’s a first look at our upcoming Arena Brawler Nubs! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2337860/Nubs/

Nubs! is an absurd arena brawler, played with you friends (or enemies). Take control of a Nub and smash everyone to nublivion with many different pickups and abilities. Coming to Steam in 2025. 

Follow Nubs! for updates: 
X (Twitter) - https://x.com/FollowNubs
Discord - https://discord.gg/nubs
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@Nubs_game
Reddit - https://www.reddit.com/r/nubs/ 
#nubs  #pcgaming  #actiongames
